                     TALLEY
           Sonny Benza.  Oh, fuck.

Talley sprints across the cul-de-sac to his nearest officer,
Jorgenson, and keys Jorgenson's shoulder mike --

                     TALLEY (CONT'D)
               (into the mike)
           Leigh?  Metzger, answer me!

                     METZGER'S VOICE
           I'm at the hospital.

                     TALLEY
           Put a guard on Smith!  I want you with
